{"tid":618380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國1939年紀錄片曝光: 講述大豆源於中國，卻由美國發揚光大","createTime":"2018-04-05T19:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T06:47:44.000Z","uid":14918,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4228602b3c2af6f2827795445ca2e5934e968ae5","tid":618380,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T19:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/030129_53434ae366d943b52bbdec99a9da9697.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F030129_53434ae366d943b52bbdec99a9da9697.png&h=e74ecce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n農業與科學本來就是不可分割的學科<br />\n<br />\n中國視大豆為食物，製造醬油的原材料，但在1939年美國科學家卻研究大豆如何在農業和經濟上產生作用。<br />\n<br />\n條片講述自20世界以來，美國如何利用化學技術，製成幾百種不同的消費者產品了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cimg2.163.com/auto/2007/7/18/200707180924394baa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcimg2.163.com%2Fauto%2F2007%2F7%2F18%2F200707180924394baa5.jpg&h=780f6a21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n例如現今Ford （福特）的Mustang (野馬）跑車座椅就是以大豆萃取物為原料製成，還成為Ford以後製造座椅的標準。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n現今大豆的用途已經遍布各行各業，包括橡膠、纖維、油墨、有機溶料、塑料、潤滑添加劑、粘合劑、食物、製紙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zD0MY6UwypI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzD0MY6UwypI&d=B9bpgYy%2BZWA%2Fd5tY0mLm0dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=39a90d76\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zD0MY6UwypI</a>"},{"pid":"737efcc6114e138310e9fcc5c1b177cd4617c0de","tid":618380,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T23:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52577056f6216f56b1ee8dfb833adab4c176f106","tid":618380,"uid":57376,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T23:29:34.000Z","msg":"有邊樣野唔係鬼佬發揚光大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smil